    'vulnerability_scan + critical_cve_detected are referenced by seven framework YAMLs (CIS, DORA, ISO27001, NIS2, NIST, PCI-DSS, SOC2). Until you upload here, every one of those frameworks ignores the vulnerability dimension. One upload moves all seven scores at once.': 'vulnerability_scan + critical_cve_detected son referenciados por siete YAMLs de marcos (CIS, DORA, ISO27001, NIS2, NIST, PCI-DSS, SOC2). Hasta que no cargue aquí, todos esos marcos ignoran la dimensión de vulnerabilidad. Una carga mueve las siete puntuaciones a la vez.',
